cardutil
========
Cardutil is a python library and set of tools for working with payment card messages and files.

The library currently has no dependencies.

Getting started
---------------

### install
    $ python setup.py develop

### test
    $ python setup.py test
    
### docs
    $ pip install sphinx
    $ sphinx-apidoc -o ./docs/source  ./cardutil 
    $ make html -C ./docs
    $ open ./docs/build/html/index.html 

libraries
---------

### iso8583 
ISO8583 message parser allows you to read and write ISO8583 messages.

Supports Mastercard PDS field structures.

### mciipm
Mastercard IPM clearing file processors for
* block and unblock 1014 blocked IPM and parameter files
* process VBS format records


tools
-----
The following command line utilities are installed as part of the package

